<br>
She gives you what looks like a ticket stub, which you give to Xjari. Now, unfortunately my screenshots let me down and I missed the first bit of what she says, but here is the rest:<br>
<br>
Acolyte Xjari V’lyr says ‘………you have earned some minor and very precious trust from us. The purpose of your tasks, outsider, has been to aid us infinding a very rare material known as [Night Ember].’<br>
Your faction standing with Primordial Malice got better.<br>
