Your faction standing with Dark Bargainers got worse.<br>
Your faction standing with Dismal Rage got worse.<br>
Your faction standing with Shadowknights of Night Keep got worse.<br>
You gain party experience!!<br>
<br>
She gives you 3 pieces of powdered night ember.<br>
